leads to the correct field line configuration for two alice fluxes in
the presence of a charge. Figure (a) shows a single charge in figure
(b) a pair of fluxes is created in the vicinity of the charge but with
the wrong field line pattern as follows from deforming -gauge
sheet, figure (c). The correct field line pattern is given in figure
